*The number of generations is not arbitrary. It is the Euler characteristic of the SU(3) mode manifold — the same object that gives three colors via its fixed points and three independent representations via its cohomology ring.*

*Two mysteries of the Standard Model — why three colors, why three generations, why they're equal — are the same geometric fact viewed from different angles.*

